    <title>git status中文乱码</title>
    <link href="https://hysg.github.io/2017/06/22/67f6feda6b2616888986268f97d926b9.html"/>
    <id>https://hysg.github.io/2017/06/22/67f6feda6b2616888986268f97d926b9.html</id>
    <published>2017-06-22T03:15:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-07-05T17:06:17.074Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>有时使用命令<code>git status</code>时候会乱码。这只是把中文转换成了Unicode编码了。<br><a id="more"></a><br><img src="https://hysgsta.b0.upaiyun.com/img/2017/6/23/1.png!img" alt="git status乱码"></p>
<p>解决也很简单，只需要一条命令。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git config --global core.quotepath false</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>这样中文就不会乱码了。</p>
<p><img src="https://hysgsta.b0.upaiyun.com/img/2017/6/23/2.png!img" alt="git status乱码"></p>
]]></content>
    
